OL,6,FHSBC has bought the UK arm of collapsed
OL,7,FSilicon Valley Bank (SVB) after the
OL,8,FGovernment and Bank of England stepped
OL,9,Fin to "facilitate" a private sale.
OL,11,FThe Government said the buyout "ensures
OL,12,Fcustomer deposits are protected and can
OL,13,Fbank as normal, with no taxpayer
OL,14,Fsupport".
OL,16,FSilicon Valley Bank, a leading
OL,17,Ftech-focused bank that is heavily
OL,18,Finvolved in financing start-up firms,
OL,19,Fwas shut down in the US on Friday and
OL,20,Fits British arm was set to be wound up
OL,21,Fover the weekend.
